{"tid":1062573,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(日本) 兩小六女生疑跳樓亡　留多封遺書稱遭欺凌尋死","createTime":"2019-03-15T07:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T10:21:43.000Z","uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04866e378412b8d61d332285239f718977a627fb","tid":1062573,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190313/photo/bkn-20190313190047164-0313_00912_001_02b.jpg?20190314011453\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190313%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190313190047164-0313_00912_001_02b.jpg%3F20190314011453&h=ca24ccb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本愛知縣豐田市陣中町一座住宅大廈，周二（12日）晚上有兩名小學6年級女生被發現滿身鮮血倒臥在大廈旁的空地，疑由高處墮下，她們送院後證實死亡。警方在現場發現她們的隨身物品以及多封遺書，部分內容提及曾遭受欺凌及擔心前途，警方循自殺方向調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n據報事發於當地時間晚上7時左右，兩名女生年約12歲，都不是事發大廈的居民。豐田市教育委員會證實，死者就讀同一間公立小學的不同班級。當日上午死者都如常上課，並原定在本月20日出席畢業禮。<br />\n<br />\n對於有關女生被欺凌，教委方面則表示「不能確認」。至於死者生前就讀的小學，已於周三（13日）上午召集全體小六學生，由校長集體輔導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190313/bkn-20190313190047164-0313_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190313%2Fbkn-20190313190047164-0313_00912_001.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=de2a414f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190313/bkn-20190313190047164-0313_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"49a90c676e8ba0d03046ded03bbdc85188838d66","tid":1062573,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"連登日膠準備維穩"},{"pid":"7870e3a6019de253b73516b5448e221633fa0796","tid":1062573,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:44:55.000Z","msg":"Rip......"},{"pid":"ccc72566e5d38a20b8c713bac7a6a02694d288ae","tid":1062573,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"對於有關女生被欺凌，<span style=\"color: red;\">教委方面則表示「不能確認」</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2685d5302ed0bcac698fdbaf56fc6f72c5680f8","tid":1062573,"uid":38426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:34:40.000Z","msg":"丁可欣"},{"pid":"d124fb5973f4bf007bcf77e9ee47fcb63311093b","tid":1062573,"uid":196099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"應該每間學校都播3年A班"},{"pid":"1193ac17d5c6ec9217c1018b4ab36cf0ccb78459","tid":1062573,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}